display.description: Just tells the bot to copy your message using plain text or embed.
display.arguments:
`<mode>` ***=*** **-orig** if in plain text or **-embd** if in embed
<message> ***=*** The messaged to be copied.
display.example:
> For displaying in plain text.
```$display -orig hello world```
> For displaying inside embed.
```$display -embd hello world```

randomnum.description:
Returns a random number.
**+** For addition
**-** For subtraction
randomnum.arguments:
`<start>` ***=*** The number to start with.
<stop> ***=*** The number to stop.
randomnum.example:
> Checking if you get lucky or not.
```$randomnum 6 7```
